headline: JBM Exclusively Lists Solaya - Class A Apartments in the Heart of Orlando, FL
summary: JBM® Institutional Multifamily Advisors has exclusively listed Solaya – a Class A, elevator serviced, four-story multifamily community in Orlando, FL. The 2018-built Property is comprised of 322 units averaging 1,056 square feet and is located on 16.26 acres +/-.
